Package: globalmacrodata
Title: Global Macro Database R Package
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Karsten", "Müller", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "karsten.mueller@nus.edu.sg"),
    person("Chenzi", "Xu", role = "aut"),
    person("Mohamed", "Lehbib", role = "aut"),
    person("Ziliang", "Chen", role = "aut")
Description: This R package provides access to the Global Macro Database from Müller, Xu, Lehbib, and Chen (2025), which introduces a panel dataset of 46 macroeconomic variables across 243 countries from historical records beginning in the year 1086 until 2024, including projections through the year 2030.
